The authorization, approval, renewal, modification, or extension of any experimental, pilot, or demonstration project under 
              section 1115 of the Social Security Act (
              42 U.S.C. 1315
            ) that waives compliance with a requirement of 
              section 407 of such Act (
              42 U.S.C. 607
            ) through a waiver of 
              section 402 of such Act (
              42 U.S.C. 602
            ).
